data.description: VA ASSUMABLE 2.8% - Charming-century bungalow has been beautifully renovated & offers a cozy retreat in a quiet neighborhood. This home is perfect for first-time buyers, down-sizers, or investors looking for a rare find in this sought-after area. Conveniently located near Midtown, Central Gardens, The Children's Museum, The Museum of Science & History, and the University of Memphis. Don't miss out on this opportunity to own a lovely home in in a desirable location. Schedule your showing today!
